<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- STYLING SHEET -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/challenges/sort-challenge/sort-challenge.css" />

  <!-- JAVASCRIPT LINKS -->
  <script src="/js/challenges/quick-sort.js" defer></script>

  <title>Archibong | <%- title %>
  </title>
</head>

<body>
  <section class="sort-challenge-section">

    <article class="sort-challenge-inner">

      <div class="description">
        <h2>QUICK SORT</h2>
        <h4>Quicksort is an in-place sorting algorithm. Developed by British computer scientist Tony Hoare in 1959 and published in
        1961, it is still a commonly used algorithm for sorting. When implemented well, it can be somewhat faster than merge
        sort and about two or three times faster than heapsort.!</h4>

        <h4 class="detail-warning">N/B: <span>Array Length must be less than <b>10</b> and Number range must be less
            than <b>999</b></span></h4>

        <h4>Generate Random Numbers:</h4>
      </div>

      <div class="input-section">
        <label>Array Length:
          <input type="text" class="max-limit quick-max-limit" maxlength="2"
            placeholder="enter number within range 0 - 10. e.g  9" />
        </label>
        <label>Number Range:
          <input type="text" class="max-range quick-max-range" maxlength="3"
            placeholder="enter number within range 0 - 999. e.g 200" />
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="generate-button sort-challenge-buttons">
        <button class="generate-number-button quick-generate-number-button" type="submit">Generate</button>
      </div>

      <div class="generated-numbers quick-generated-numbers"></div>

      <div class="sort-button sort-challenge-buttons">
        <button class="sort-number-button quick-sort-number-button" type="submit">Quick Sort</button>
      </div>

      <div class="sorted-result quick-sorted-result"></div>
    </article>

  </section>
</body>

</html>